		<!-- message -->
		<div><a href="http://www.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.aspx?FN=wow-general&amp;T=12358&amp;P=1&amp;ReplyCount=116#post12358" target="_blank">http://www.worldofwarcraft.com/thre...t=116#post12358</a><br />
<br />
<br />
Scroll down a little to get to the meat of it.<br />
<br />
<br />
The gist is bascially someone is spreading a rumor that bliz is wanting to put in a system where if you play past a certain amount of time you would have to go to a tavern and &quot;relax&quot; to reduce character fatigue.  If you didn't there might be a small xp penalty.  Perhaps if you did there would be a bonus but no penalty if you didn't.  Who the hell knows because there is no offical word only rumors.<br />
<br />
Anyone of you insiders know anything about this?</div>
