		<!-- message -->
		<div>Forcing people to take a break (though it's not really forcing, since if there was a penalty it would be very small) is not a bad thing.  Quite the contrary actually.  It's called MMO- fatigue, and it's a very real problem for some people that just don't know how to stop.  I think people really underestimate the stress they put their bodies through when they do leveling sessions like that.  I myself have never and will never do something like that, but I know people that have.  It's pretty unhealthy.  I'm glad they're concerned about the welfare of their players and I really think you need to give it a chance and see it through. <br />
<br />
Personally I haven't heard anything officially about this.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
